OL,3,CThames Valley Police Chief Constable
OL,4,Creinstated following suspension
OL,6,FThe Chief Constable of Thames Valley
OL,7,FPolice has been reinstated twelve days
OL,8,Fafter he was suspended.
OL,10,FJason Hogg, who had been Chief
OL,11,FConstable since 2023, was suspended
OL,12,Fwhile an independent police complaints
OL,13,Finvestigation was carried out by the
OL,14,Fpolice watchdog into allegations of
OL,15,Fgross misconduct.
OL,17,FFollowing an appeal, Mr Hogg is now
OL,18,Fback in post.
