OL,3,CThames Valley Police Chief Constable
OL,4,Creinstated following suspension
OL,6,FThe Thames Valley Police and Crime
OL,7,FCommissioner, Matthew Barber, said he
OL,8,Fmade the suspension in the wider
OL,9,Fpublic interest to ensure confidence
OL,10,Fin the force.
OL,12,FHowever he has taken legal advice, and
OL,13,Falthough the investigation continues,
OL,14,FChief Constable Hogg has a right to
OL,15,Fremain in post, with no decisions made
OL,16,Funtil the investigation has been
OL,17,Fcompleted and scrutinised.
