OL,3,CThames Valley Police Chief Constable
OL,4,Creinstated following suspension
OL,6,FIn a statement, Thames Valley Police
OL,7,Fand Crime Commissioner Matthew Barber
OL,8,Fsaid: "I can announce today that Jason
OL,9,FHogg is returning to his duties as
OL,10,FChief Constable of Thames Valley
OL,11,Fpolice with immediate effect.
OL,13,F"Twelve days ago (16/01), when
OL,14,Fpresented with a set of allegations by
OL,15,Fthe Independent Office of Police
OL,16,FConduct (IOPC), I announced the Chief
OL,17,FConstable's suspension. Whilst I took
OL,18,Fthis decision in what I considered to
OL,19,Fbe the wider public interest of
OL,20,Fensuring confidence in policing, this
OL,21,Fhas been subject to an appeal.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
