OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F418A1738249282
OL,3,CThames Valley Police Chief Constable
OL,4,Creinstated following suspension
OL,6,F"Following these representations as
OL,7,Fpart of the normal review of such
OL,8,Fdecisions and having taken legal
OL,9,Fadvice on the appeal, it is clear that
OL,10,Fin my original suspension decision I
OL,11,Fwas over reliant on the assessment
OL,12,Fmade by the IOPC.
OL,14,F"My intention was, and remains, to
OL,15,Fensure that the highest standards of
OL,16,Fconduct are maintained at every level
OL,17,Fof policing and to give the public
OL,18,Freassurance in policing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
