OL,3,CThames Valley Police Chief Constable
OL,4,Creinstated following suspension
OL,6,F"Whilst the IOPC will continue their
OL,7,Finvestigation, I am pleased to be able
OL,8,Fto reinstate the Chief Constable to
OL,9,Fcontinue his work leading Thames
OL,10,FValley Police. I have always had
OL,11,Fconfidence in Jason Hogg as Chief
OL,12,FConstable and I look forward to
OL,13,Fcontinuing working in partnership with
OL,14,Fhim on behalf of communities in Thames
OL,15,FValley.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
