OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F418A1738249282
OL,3,CThames Valley Police Chief Constable
OL,4,Creinstated following suspension
OL,6,F"Undoubtedly, the allegations and the
OL,7,Fsuspension have created great
OL,8,Funcertainty within Thames Valley
OL,9,FPolice. I am confident however that,
OL,10,Fbuilding on the strong working
OL,11,Frelationship that we have developed
OL,12,Fover many years, the Chief Constable
OL,13,Fand I will continue to work closely to
OL,14,Fprotect our communities across the
OL,15,FThames Valley by continuing to cut
OL,16,Fcrime and catch more criminals."
